sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant HTTPServer as HTTP Server (FastAPI)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant gRPCServer as gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant PredictSvc as GlobalPredictServicer
    participant TrainSvc as GlobalTrainServicer
    participant ModelMgr as ModelManager
    participant LoadedModel as LoadedModel<br/>(Module.run)
    participant ModelMesh as Model Mesh Sidecar<br/>Unix socket / 8085/TCP
    participant ModelLoader as CoreModelLoader
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8086/TCP HTTP
    participant OTEL as OTEL Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client, OTEL: Flow 1: HTTP Inference (Unary or SSE Streaming)

    Client->>HTTPServer: POST /api/v1/{task}/{model_id}<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    HTTPServer->>PredictSvc: route request (in-process)
    PredictSvc->>ModelMgr: retrieve_model(model_id)
    ModelMgr->>LoadedModel: Module.run(input)
    LoadedModel-->>ModelMgr: prediction result
    ModelMgr-->>PredictSvc: result
    PredictSvc-->>HTTPServer: response
    HTTPServer-->>Client: JSON response or SSE stream<br/>Optional TLS

    Note over Client, OTEL: Flow 2: gRPC Inference

    Client->>gRPCServer: {TaskName}Service.{TaskName}Predict<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    gRPCServer->>PredictSvc: CaikitRuntimeServerWrapper<br/>dynamic RPC routing
    PredictSvc->>ModelMgr: retrieve_model(model_id)
    ModelMgr->>LoadedModel: Module.run(input)
    LoadedModel-->>ModelMgr: prediction result
    ModelMgr-->>PredictSvc: result
    PredictSvc-->>gRPCServer: response proto
    gRPCServer-->>Client: gRPC response<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS

    Note over Client, OTEL: Flow 3: Model Loading via Model Mesh

    ModelMesh->>gRPCServer: loadModel(model_id, model_path)<br/>gRPC (Unix socket or 8085/TCP)
    gRPCServer->>ModelMgr: ModelRuntimeServicer.loadModel
    ModelMgr->>ModelLoader: load_model(model_path)
    alt Local model path
        ModelLoader->>FS: Read model artifacts<br/>Local I/O
        FS-->>ModelLoader: model files
    else S3 model path
        ModelLoader->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, IAM auth
        S3-->>ModelLoader: model files
    end
    ModelLoader-->>ModelMgr: loaded Module instance
    ModelMgr-->>gRPCServer: LoadModelResponse(size)
    gRPCServer-->>ModelMesh: success + model size

    Note over Client, OTEL: Flow 4: Training Job

    Client->>HTTPServer: POST /api/v1/{module}/train<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS (multipart form)
    HTTPServer->>TrainSvc: route training request
    TrainSvc->>LoadedModel: Module.train(data) [async]
    LoadedModel->>FS: Save training output<br/>Local filesystem
    FS-->>LoadedModel: saved
    LoadedModel-->>TrainSvc: training_id
    TrainSvc-->>HTTPServer: training_id
    HTTPServer-->>Client: {training_id: "..."}

    Client->>HTTPServer: GET /api/v1/training/status<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    HTTPServer-->>Client: {status: "COMPLETED"}

    Note over Client, OTEL: Observability (continuous)

    Prometheus->>gRPCServer: GET /metrics<br/>8086/TCP HTTP (plaintext)
    gRPCServer-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics

    gRPCServer->>OTEL: Push traces<br/>4317/TCP gRPC, Optional TLS/mTLS
    HTTPServer->>OTEL: Push traces<br/>4317/TCP gRPC, Optional TLS/mTLS
